<div
	layout="row"
    ng-show="active == 'profile'">
              
               
	<md-input-container  class="md-block" flex-gt-xs>
		<label>Name</label>
		<input ng-model="profile.name" md-maxlength="25">
	</md-input-container>
	<md-input-container  class="md-block" flex-gt-xs>
		<label>Image</label>
		<input ng-model="profile.imageUrl" md-maxlength="50">
	</md-input-container>
	<md-input-container  class="md-block" flex-gt-xs>
		<label>Twitter Name</label>
		<input ng-model="profile.twitterName" md-maxlength="25">
	</md-input-container>
	<md-input-container  class="md-block" flex-gt-xs>
		<label>Game Tag</label>
		<input ng-model="profile.hashTag" md-maxlength="3">
	</md-input-container>
	
		
</div>
<div
	layout="row"
    ng-show="active == 'profile'">
    Änderungen werden ggf erst beim erneutem Login für dich sichtbar sein.<br>
	<md-button  ng-click="submitProfile()">speichern</md-button>
</div>
